list

  14oz can artichoke hearts
  1/2 cup mayonnaise
  1/2 cup sour cream
  8oz cream cheese
  1 1/2 cups mozzarella, shredded
  3/4 cups grated parmesan
  1/2 tsp garlic powder
  1 tsp red pepper flakes
  1 tsp black pepper

directions

  mix all ingredients
  add contents to 8x8 baking dish
  350deg oven, 35min
    broil, 2min
